Blizzard Project SCRUM Report: Week 4

Team B-Triple-J: Joseph Townsend, John Moreno, Jonathan Wang, Brandon Donohue

Our app should work on any web browser that supports WebGL.

App Features
•	Textured Earth object
•	Sprite Izzy object 
•	Sprite Arklet object
•	Camera position adjustable
•	Zoom enabled
•	Earth rotates
•	Izzy properly moves away from Earth while orbiting around it
•	Arklet follows Izzy
•	Bolids randomly generate
•	Bolids textured
•	Starry skybox
•	Bolids move towards Earth
•	Arklets generated
•	Arklets move around Izzy
•	Arklets deleted upon impact with bolid
•	Bolids delete upon impact with Earth or Izzy
•	User interface 
•	Home page 
•	Member page 
•	Overview page
•	Features page
•	Simulation tab

The app was completed on time and meets all of the requirements.
